Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:29.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}心がまだ追いついて来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}今は想像出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:37.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}この先押し寄せる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}Still,I have to keep going this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:43.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}あなたが居ない世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}miss you so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:48.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}消えないこの鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:52.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}会いたいあの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:58.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}もう一度近づきたい話したい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:24:01.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}I know life can be so hard.
